                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "sígate de mis ojos la corriente;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+----+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "y, aunque de paso, tanto fuego ardiente",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
